WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.850
I first became interested in joining the military back in the day when

00:00:05.850 --> 00:00:10.850
 my father used to come back from his work in his uniform from the army,

00:00:10.850 --> 00:00:15.850
 and he'd tell me about all of the things that he had experienced.

00:00:15.850 --> 00:00:20.850
 I grew up in the fifth sixth and seventh grade and part of the eighth

00:00:20.850 --> 00:00:25.850
 grade in Germany, and although I didn't really see the military

00:00:25.850 --> 00:00:30.850
 part of it, I did see some of the things that like you could have outside

00:00:30.850 --> 00:00:35.850
 of the work. So I saw the nice house that you could live in,

00:00:35.850 --> 00:00:40.850
 I saw the cool car that he was driving, I saw many times you know people

00:00:40.850 --> 00:00:45.850
 PTing, exercising outside, PT is physical training. So I kind of

00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:50.850
 got the impression of like what the military lifestyle would be like

00:00:50.850 --> 00:00:55.850
 compared to all the civilian lifestyles that I saw back where I'm

00:00:55.850 --> 00:01:00.850
 from, and I gotta say it was really impressive.

